sp.p:
Yes, and the Vinegar-bottle his man too: but now I think 
on it he shall excuse me, 
I will loose no time; 
if I win, I shall have less cause to repent, if I loose, 
by these hilts I will make him the cause and beat him.

Master Hazard, I was afraid you had been gone, 
 there is a fresh Gamester come in with his pockets full of Gold; 
he dazzles the Gamesters, and no man has stock to play with him.
